{"tid":1857690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工信部稱口罩生產已恢復六成　惟物資產能未滿足需求","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:14:43.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e73b7b8461393242683eb579d8a61ff150655685","tid":1857690,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"工信部稱口罩生產已恢復六成 惟物資產能未滿足需求<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1506188_1_L_20200202150121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1506188_1_L_20200202150121.jpg&h=419ec624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃利斌說，重點醫療防護用品，供應依然緊張。（國新辦網頁）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在北京，工信部運行監測協調局局長黃利斌說，目前國內口罩實際產能，已恢復60%。他說工信部點算過各地消毒及防護等物資的數量，包括醫學用防護衣及N95口罩，發現重點醫療防護用品，供應依然緊張，口罩等物資的產能，未能滿足需求，只能優先保障湖北及省內的重災區武漢。<br />\n<br />\n水利部就向全國水利系統發出緊急通知，要求做好部署，在防控疫情期間，全面保障農村供水安全、做好水質淨化消毒及水質檢測工作、加強管理水利工程，確保安全運作。"},{"pid":"b8a38da4d0ff2afe713e726aff2a264be826ab97","tid":1857690,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡（型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857672</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9CLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=7632eff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手正評，避免沉底"},{"pid":"77db6daabbc5c6e34e00699b39681f9af00a3b9d","tid":1857690,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}